  body
  .container
    .page-header
      h1 So Coded balloon lights admin
      p.lead Athorized people can trigger different effects on our so coded balloon lights system here.
      h3 Just press a button and watch the lights
      p Effects triggered here, block any user interaction.
    .row
      .col-md-12
          each _fn, effect in effects
            form(action='/effect/'+effect, method='post')
              button.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg.btn-block(type='submit')= effect
    
